  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Paraido is a relaxing yet challenging puzzle game.<br>Complete levels by moving and rotating the puzzle pieces into their correct positions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jigsaw Mode</h2>Use the pieces to completely fill the game board.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maze Mode</h2>Build the longest maze possible from the pieces you are given.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 70 unique levels</h2>Challenge yourself by completing the ever more increasingly difficult levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Includes Level Editor</h2>This game comes with a built-in level editor. Create your own levels or browse levels created by others!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/99162e031704700896b3410d9fdeb669.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Paraido is a relaxing yet challenging puzzle game.<br>Complete levels by moving and rotating the puzzle pieces into their correct positions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jigsaw Mode</h2>Use the pieces to completely fill the game board.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maze Mode</h2>Build the longest maze possible from the pieces you are given.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/f35f0149e87433facd80e7b9bbe38732.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 70 unique levels</h2>Challenge yourself by completing the ever more increasingly difficult levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Includes Level Editor</h2>This game comes with a built-in level editor. Create your own levels or browse levels created by others!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.poster.avif?t=1702326568\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.webm?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564950/extras/b2e50c2a31295a44a3576758de6c1335.mp4?t=1702326568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
